  "bodyText": "MiniMax 2.7 & Kimi K2.5 are free on Zo Zo · Pricing About Newsletter Blog Resources Download Get started Back to Skills Run in Zo shorten Shorten URLs using is.gd (no auth required). Returns a permanent short link. Clawdbot Notice On Zo, the script lives at shorten.sh . Shorten Quickly shorten URLs using the is.gd service. No API key or account required. Usage /home/art/clawd/skills/shorten/shorten.sh \"https://example.com/very/long/url\" Copy Examples Standard usage: shorten \"https://google.com\" # Output: https://is.gd/O5d2Xq Copy With custom alias (if supported by script extension later): Currently basic shortening only. Notes Links are permanent. No analytics dashboard (simple redirect). Rate limits apply (be reasonable). Preview - Open in Zo to view the full skill. PRODUCT Documentation Blog Newsletter Comparisons Pricing Skills Integrations Channels Models Product Updates INFORMATION FAQ Careers Brand Terms Privacy Help Center Contact Security COMMUNITY Discord LinkedIn X @zocomputer YouTube Testimonials Ambassadors Merch Zo Computer Company"
